headerText.line1: Gukora igikorwa kibanziriza kwiyandikisha ku muntu umwe cyangwa benshi, Uzuza amakuru y'ibanze uahyireho n'ibyangombwa bisabwa. Gusaba gahunda, hitamo aho wifuza kwiyandikishiriza, itariki n'umunsi. Igikorwa kibanziriza kwiyandikisa nikigenda neza, murabona ubutumwa kuri imeri cyangwa kuri nomero ya telephone.
headerText.line2: Kanda ku bika bikurikira kugirango ubone amakuru ahagije ajyanye no kuzuza ifishi y'igikorwa kibanziriza kwiyandikisha.

select_language.name: Hitamo ururimi ushaka

list.line1: Ku ipaji yo kwinjira muri konti yawe, kanda ku kamenyetso kareba hasi ku rurimi kugirango ubone ilisiti y'indimi

select_language.note: Icyitonderwa: Amazina y'ibyo mwuzuza mu tuzu, aho mwibeshye n'ubutumwa ku makuru bujyanye n'iki gikorwa cyo kwiyandikisha muragenda mubibona mu rurimi mwahisemo.

login.name: Kwinjira muri konti

list.line1: Ku ipaji yo kwinjira muri konti yawe, injiza imeri cyangwa nomero ya telefone mu kazu ka emeri ID cyangwa aka nomero ya telefone.
list.line3: Kanda kohereza OTP kugirango ubone ijambobanga rikoreshwa rimwe (OTP) kuri imeri cyangwa nomero ya telefone mwatanze.
list.line4: Injiza OTP (ijambobanga rikoreshwa rimwe) mu kazu ka OTP ubundi ukande kuri genzura.

login.note: Icyitonderwa: Mu gihe mutabonye OTP, kanda kongera kohereza kugirango mubone indi OTP. Injiza OTP (ijambobanga rikoreshwa rimwe) nshya mwabonye.
login.line: Iyo OTP yagenzuwe, ushobora gukora, kureba cyangwa ugahindura ubusabe bw'igikorwa kibanziriza kwiyandikisha.

select_data_capture_language.name: Hitamo ururimi rwo gufatamo amakuru

list.line1: Umuntu winjiye muri sisitemu bwa mbere kandi adafite ubusabe azajya asabwa guhitamo ururimi rwo gufatamo amakuru ye. Izondimi nizo zizakoreshwa ubutaha ku bundi busabe bwose buzakorwa mu ako kanya.
list.line2: Ururimi ukoresha sisitemu yahisemo yinjira muri konti nirwo ruzatoranywamo nk'ururimi rwo gufatamo amakuru
list.line3: Ukoresha sisitemu ashobora kubihindura akanze kuri hindura ururimi rwo gufatamo amakuru

select_data_capture_language.note: Icyitonderwa: Aya mahitamo araboneka gusa ari uko ushinzwe gutanga indangamuntu (ID) yashyizemo uburyo bwo gukoresha izindi ndimi.

t&c.name: Emeza Amategeko n' Amabwiriza

list.line1: Ku ipaji y'amakuru y'abanze, uragirwa inama yo kubanza gusoma amategeko n' amabwiriza ukavivura akazu ka ndabyemeye. Icyi cyemezo n'icyo kutwemerera kubika no gukoresha amakuru akwerekeyeho.
list.line2: Kanda ndabyemeye kugirango ubyemere ubundi wuzuze amakuru y'ibanze.

t&c.note: Icyitonderwa: Ukoresha sisitemu ni itegeko ko agomba kutwemerera gukoresha amakuru amwerekeyeho mu gukora cyangwa kuvugurura ubusabe. Ibigize ubusabe bizajya bigaragazwa mu ndimi zose zo gufata amakuru

demographic.name: Uzuza amakuru y'ibanze

list.line1: Uzuza amakuru yose y'ibanze akwerekeyeho, harimo amazina, imyaka ufite/ itariki y'amavuko, igitsina, utuye mu Rwanda nka, aderesi, nomero ya telefone na imeri ID, n'ibindi.
list.line1_note: Icyitonderwa: Mushobora kwinjiza imyaka mufite cyangwa mukinjiza itariki yanyu y'amavuko.
list.line2: Mushobora no guhindura cyangwa mukagenzura amakuru yanyu y'ibanze mu rurimi rwa kabiri i buryo.
list.line3: Nyuma yo kuzuza no kugenzura amakuru yanyu y'ibanze, kanda komeza ushyireho ibyangombwa byawe.

demographic.line: Icyitonderwa: Amazina y'ibyo mwuzuza mu tuzu, aho mwibeshye n'ubutumwa ku makuru bujyanye n'iki gikorwa cyo kwiyandikisha muragenda mubibona mu rurimi mwahisemo.

list.line1: Ku ipaji yo gushyiraho ibyangombwa, hitamo ibyangombwa (urugero: pasiporo, indangamuntu, n'ibindi) ku kamenyetso kareba hasi ka lisiti y'ibyangombwa ku byangombwa byose bikenewe.
list.line2: Kanda gushakisha kugirango ufungure akazu ko gushaka aho ibyangombwa bibitse kuri mudasobwa yawe cyangwa ahandi waba warabitse ibyangombwa bisikannye.
list.line4: Iyo gushyiraho icyangomba byagenze neza, Icyangombwa kigaragara ku ruhande rw'iburyo. Genzura ko washyizeho icyangombwa cya nyacyo.
list.line5: Subiramo intambwe ya 1-4 kugirango ushyireho icyangombwa kuri buri bwoko bw'ibyangombwa bishoboka.
list.line6: Iyo wongeraho undi muntu usaba, niba umuntu mushya usaba yongeweho, icyangombwa k' ikizibiti cya aderesi (POA) ni kimwe n'igisanzwe ku muntu warusanzwemo, wari waramaze gushyiraho icyangombwa cye cya POA, ubundi ukande ni kimwe ubundi uhitemo amazina y'usaba.
list.line7: Iyo urangije gushyiraho ibyangombwa byose, kanda gukomeza kugirango usubiremo usuzume ubusabe bwawe.

list.line1: Ku ipaji yo gusuzuma ubusabe bwanyu, niba mushaka guhindura amakuru yanyu yibanze (amazina, imyaka, n'ibindi), kanda guhindura ku ruhande rwo hejuru iburyo ku gika cy'amakuru y'ibanze, kugirango ujye ku ipaji y'amakuru y'ibanze uhindure amakuru nk'uko bisabwa.
list.line2: Guhindura ibyangombwa mwashyizeho,kanda guhindura ku ruhande rwo hasi ku gika cy'ibyangombwa, Jya ku ipaji yo gushyiraho ibyangombwa hanyuma uhindure ibyangombwa washyizeho nk'uko bisabwa.
list.line3: Niba ushaka kongeraho usaba mushya, Kanda ongeraho usaba.
list.line3_note: Icyitonderwa: N'ukanda kongeraho usaba, urajyanwa ku ipaji y'amakuru y'ibanze kugirango utwemerere gukoresha amakuru yawe hanyuma ukomeze utange amakuru y'ibanze akenewe n'ibyangombwa.

list.line1: Ku ipaji yo gusaba gahunda, ushobora kubona aho kwiyandikishiriza unyuze muri aya mahitamo atatu akurikira:
list.line1_note: Icyitonderwa: aho kwiyandikishiriza hashoboka hahita hagaragazwa hashingiwe ku makuru y'ibanze watanze (agasanduku k'iposita)

subList.line1: Kanda aho kwiyandikishiriza hakwegereye kugirango urebe aho kwiyandikishiriza hashingiwe ku makuru y'aho mutuye.
subList.line2: Koresha akazu k'ishakiro kugirango ushake aho kwiyandikishiriza hashingiwe kucyo mushaka gushingiraho mushaka.
subList.line3: Kanda aho kwiyandikishiriza hashoboka kugirango ubone aho kwiyandikishiriza hashingiwe ku makuru yawe y'ibanze.(agasanduku k'iposita)

list.line2: Ikarita y'aho kwiyandikishiriza hatoranyijwe hagaragara ku ruhande rw'iburyo rwa ekara yanyu.
list.line3: Mukoresheje amahitamo ayo ariyo yose muri aya mahitamo atatu, hitamo aho ushaka kujya kwiyandikishiriza ubundi ukande komeza gusaba gahunda.

list.line1: Sisitemu iragaragaza urutonde rw'iminsi ihari kuri karindari n'imibare ya gahunda zihari. Hitamo itariki ushaka.
list.line2: Urutonde amasaha ahari ku itariki mwahisemo ari hagati ya mu gitondo n'ikigoroba. Hitamo igihe ushaka.
list.line4: Hitamo amazina y'usaba kugirango usabe gahunda.
list.line4_note: Icyitonderwa: Urutonde rw'usaba/abasaba rugaragara hasi i buryo.
list.line5: Genzura isaha nk'uko yatoranijwe ku izina ry'usaba/abasaba.
list.line6: Kanda Kohereza kugirango urebe icyemeza ubusabe bwawe.

list.line1: Nyuma y'uko kuzuza ubusabe bw'igikorwa kibanziriza kwiyandikisha byagenze neza, irabona icyemeza ubusabe.
list.line2: Mushobora gucapa, gusohora cyangwa kohereza icyemeza ubusabe bwanyu kuri imeri cyangwa ubutumwa bugufi.

subList.line3: Kongeraho undi muntu ubona icyemeza ubusabe, kurikiza izi ntambwe:

subList.line2: Injiza nomero ya telefone mu kazu ka nomero ya telefone na/cyangwa imeri mu kazu ko kwandikamo imeri.
subList.line3: Kanda ohereza kugirango ubone icyemeza ubusabe kuri imeri cyangwa nomero ya telefone mwatanze.

Logout.name: Sohoka

list.line1: Knada gusohoka mu nguni yo hejuru y'iburyo.
list.line2: Kanda OK kugirango usohoke mu gikorwa cy'ubusabe bw'igikorwa kibanziriza kwiyandikisha.

Logout.line: Kwinjira ukoresheje nomero ya telefone cyangwa imeri kugirango ubone uburenganzira ku busabe bwabitswe.

questions.question: Nta nomero ya telefone mfite cyangwa imeri. Ni gute nakora ubusabe bw'igikorwa kibanziriza kwiyandikisha?
questions.answer: Uahobora gukoresha nomero ya telefone cyangwa imeri y'inshuti cyangwa umuvandimwe ukinjira mu busabe bw'igikorwa kibanziriza kwiyandikisha

questions.question: Nabuze nomero ya telefone/imeri nakoresheje nkora ubusabe bw'igikorwa kibanziriza kwiyandikisha. nakora iki?
questions.answer: Kora indi konti ukoresheje nomero ya telefone cyangwa imeri nshya.

questions.question: Ni iki kiba iyo mpisemo ururimi runaka kuri ekara yo kwinjira?
questions.answer: Hitamo ururimi ushobora gusoma no kwandika byoroshye kuko ifishi yose iragaragazwa mu rurimi runaka wahisemo

questions.question: Niba ntafite ibyangombwa bikenewe mu gihe cyo kuzuza ubusabe bw'igikorwa kibanziriza kwiyandikisha?
questions.answer: Uzuza amakuru y'ibanze hanyuma ubike ubusabe. Ushobora gushyiraho ibyangombwa ikindi gihe.

questions.question: Nshobora gusaba gahunda y'abanyu babiri gusa mu bantu batanu bari ku busabe bw'igikorwa kibanziriza kwiyandikisha?
questions.answer: Yego, ushobora gusaba gahunda y'umubare runaka mu mubare wose w'abasaba.

questions.question: Bigenda bite iyo ntubahirije itariki ya gahunda?
questions.answer: Gerageza wubahirize itariki ya gahunda. Nutayubahiriza, ongera uyisabe ukoresheje uburyo bwa “Hindura”.

questions.question: Nasabye gahunda ku itariki ya 10 Gashyantare. Ese nshobora guhindura itariki ya gahunda yanjye ikaba ku itariki ya 18 Gashyantare?
questions.answer: Yego, Niba itararangiza igihe, ushobora gusaba gahunda nshya ku itariki izaza mu gihe kiri imbere.

questions.question: Nsabye gahunda aho kwiyandikishiriza hitwa Kimironko. Ese nshobora guhindura aho kwiyandikishiriza hakaba ahitwa Gisozi?
questions.answer: Oya. gusa ushobora kureka gahunda ihari ugasaba indi gahunda nshyashya mu kandi gace wahisemo.

questions.question: Nahinduye amakuru nyuma mbona icyemeza ubusabe. Ese ngomba gusohora cyangwa gucapa icyemeza ubusabe nanone?
questions.answer: Ipaji y'icyemeza ubusabe ni icyangombwa cyo kureberaho ukibuka agace n'itariki ya gahunda, n'ibindi. Aho kwiyandikishiriza, amakuru yawe mashya bazahita bayabona byihuse. Ntago ari ngombwa kongera gucapa cyangwa gusohora icyemeza ubusabe.

questions.question: Nongeye gusaba iyindi gahunda nyuma mbona icyemeza ubusabe. Ese ni ngombwa ko nongera gusohora cyangwa gucapa icyemeza ubusabe nanone?
questions.answer: Ipaji y'icyemeza ubusabe ni icyangombwa cyo kwifashisha gusa wibuka agace n'isaha ya gahunda, n'ibindi. Uahobora kongera gucapa cyangwa gusohora icyemeza ubusabe kugirango bigufashe kwibuka igihe cya gahunda yawe ariko si ngombwa kubikora.

questions.question: Ese undi muntu yakohereza ubusabe mu cyimbo cyanjye mu gihe cy'igikorwa kwiyandikisha?
questions.answer: Oya, igikorwa cyo kwiyandikisha bisaba gufata ifoto yawe n'amakuru(amafoto) y'ibice bimwe na bimwe bigize umubiri. Rero ugomba kuba uhari wowe ubwawe aho biyandikishiriza.

questions.question: Ndi kuba kure y'aho ntuye ku buryo buhoraho mu gihe cy'imyaka ibiri. Ni ikihe kimenyetso (kizibiti) cy'aho ntuye ngomba gutanga?
questions.answer: GoM izafata umwanzuro w'ikibazo n'ibisubizo bikwiriye.

questions.question: Ntago mfite ikimenyetso cya aderesi y'aho ntuye ubu. Nakora iki?
questions.answer: GoM izafata umwanzuro w'ikibazo n'ibisubizo bikwiriye.

questions.question: Nta byangombwa na bimwe mfite. Nakora iki?
questions.answer: GoM izafata umwanzuro w'ikibazo n'ibisubizo bikwiriye.

questions.question: Ni iminsi ingahe mbere nareka cyangwa nkasaba indi gahunda y'ubusabe?
questions.answer: GoM izafata umwanzuro w'ikibazo n'ibisubizo bikwiriye.

questions.question: Ese ni ngombwa kwitwaza ibyangombwa bya orijinali cyangwa ibifotoje byasinyweho na noteri igihe nje aho biyandikishiriza?
questions.answer: GoM izafata umwanzuro w'ikibazo n'ibisubizo bikwiriye
